{"amendement": {"@xmlns": "http://schemas.assemblee-nationale.fr/referentiel", "uid": "AMANR5L17PO59051B0134P0D1N000072", "chronotag": "1739874519613", "legislature": "17", "identification": {"numeroLong": "CL72", "numeroOrdreDepot": "72", "prefixeOrganeExamen": "CION_LOIS", "numeroRect": "0"}, "examenRef": "EXANR5L17PO59051B0134P0D1", "texteLegislatifRef": "PIONANR5L17B0134", "triAmendement": "jcaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaco", "cardinaliteAmdtMultiples": "1", "amendementParentRef": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "signataires": {"auteur": {"typeAuteur": "D\u00e9put\u00e9", "gouvernementRef": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "acteurRef": "PA795998", "groupePolitiqueRef": "PO845514", "auteurRapporteurOrganeRef": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}}, "cosignataires": {"acteurRef": "PA721896"}, "suffixe": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "libelle": "Mme&#160;K/Bidi et Mme&#160;Faucillon"}, "pointeurFragmentTexte": {"partieAmendableRef": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "division": {"titre": "Article 14", "articleDesignationCourte": "ART. 14", "articleDesignation": "ARTICLE 14", "type": "ARTICLE", "avant_A_Apres": "A", "divisionRattachee": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "articleAdditionnel": "false", "chapitreAdditionnel": "false", "urlDivisionTexteVise": "/17/textes/0134.asp#D_Article_14"}, "amendementStandard": {"alinea": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}}}, "corps": {"cartoucheInformatif": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "contenuAuteur": {"dispositif": "<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Supprimer cet article.</p>", "avantAppel": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "exposeSommaire": "<p>Les auteurs de cet amendement sont oppos&#x00E9;s &#x00E0; la d&#x00E9;lictualisation de l&#x2019;oubli par n&#x00E9;gligence d&#x2019;objets et de bagages dans les transports en commun (2 500 euros d&#x2019;amende) et de l&#x2019;abandon volontaire d&#x2019;objets ou de bagages (3 750 euros d&#x2019;amende).</p><p>Ils rappellent que les articles L2242-4 et R2241-13 du code des transports permettent d&#x00E9;j&#x00E0; de r&#x00E9;primer ces faits. Si l&#x2019;oubli de bagage n&#x2019;a pas eu de cons&#x00E9;quences sur le trafic, il est sanctionn&#x00E9; d&#x2019;une contravention de quatri&#x00E8;me classe. En revanche, si l&#x2019;oubli a entra&#x00EE;n&#x00E9; des cons&#x00E9;quences sur le trafic des trains, la peine encourue est de 3 750 euros d&#x2019;amende et six mois de prison.</p><p>La cr&#x00E9;ation de ces nouveaux d&#x00E9;lits appara&#x00EE;t ainsi inutile et disproportionn&#x00E9;e.</p><p>Enfin, la sanction de l&#x2019;oubli involontaire para&#x00EE;t particuli&#x00E8;rement d&#x00E9;mesur&#x00E9;e et la preuve de l&#x2019;intentionnalit&#x00E9; sera, dans les faits, difficile &#x00E0; apporter.</p>", "annexeExposeSommaire": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}}}, "cycleDeVie": {"dateDepot": "2024-11-22", "datePublication": "2024-11-27", "soumisArticle40": "false", "etatDesTraitements": {"etat": {"code": "DI", "libelle": "Discut\u00e9"}, "sousEtat": {"code": "DI", "libelle": "Non soutenu"}}, "dateSort": "2024-11-27T17:14:20+01:00", "sort": "Non soutenu"}, "representations": {"representation": {"nom": "PDF", "typeMime": {"type": "application", "subType": "PDF"}, "statutRepresentation": {"verbatim": "true", "canonique": "true", "officielle": "true", "transcription": "false", "enregistrement": "false"}, "repSource": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "offset": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "contenu": {"documentURI": "/base/AMANR5L17PO59051B0134P0D1N000072?format=pdf"}, "dateDispoRepresentation": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}}}, "seanceDiscussionRef": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "article99": "false", "loiReference": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "discussionCommune": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "discussionIdentique": {"idDiscussion": "74350", "typePosition": "Milieu"}, "accordGouvernementDepotHorsDelai": "Sans objet"}}